"1  (7-ounce) can chipotle peppers in adobo sauce, undrained","2 pounds lean ground beef","2 teaspoons steak seasoning","1/2  (10-ounce) package Cheddar cheese, cut into 4 thick (1.25-ounce) slices","4  sesame seed hamburger buns","  Toppings: tomato slices, red onion slices, romaine lettuce leaves, yellow mustard, mayonnaise"